<br>
Kazen and his apprentice Emkel are near the stone skeleton toweer approx loc +340,-1600. Speak to Kazen and say &quot; I wish to study the dark arts&quot; At this point follow the prompts and he will tell you that you need to find and kill Sir Edwin Motte and return his head.<br>
<br>
Sir Edwin Motte is located in the tavern by the docks in East Freeport and is on rotation spawn with the bard and a few others.<br>
<br>
Return his head to Kazen and he will give you a symbol of the apprentice. He then tells you that when you receive a symbol speak its name in order to receive more information. Now say &quot; I have the symbol of the apprentice&quot; He then tells you about the DE necro in Nektulos that sent you to him. Take the symbol to her and bring Kazen the reagents she is collecting.<br>
<br>
Return to Nektulos and give the symbol to her. She will then tell you that she does not trust you , in order to get her reagents you must kill a magician that wears the same robe as her. She is referring to Najena. She also gives you a twisted symbol of the apprentice.<br>
<br>
Now obtain an FBR<br>
<br>
Return to Nektulos and give the DE necro the FBR and she will give you the reagents and tell you to take the symbol and reagents to Kazens lapdog. She is referring to Ekmel.<br>
<br>
Return to Lake Rathe and give the reagents and the symbol to Ekmal. He then gives you the symbol of the serpent. Say to Ekmal &quot; I have the symbol of the serpent&quot; Ekmel will then instruct you to head to Kunark to find an herbalist named Ssessthrass and retrieve an herb from him. He also warns you about Ssessthrass and tells you to show him the symbol to prove your loyalty.<br>
<br>
Head to the swamp of no hope Ssessthrass is near the FoB zone approx loc +3800,+1200. Give him the symbol of the serpent. He will then give you the scaled symbol of the serpent and tell you I do not have the herb and that the sarnaks guard it and only royals partake of it in Chardok and to bring it back and the symbol.<br>
<br>
Go to Chardok and kill the herbalist and loot the herb on him Return this to Ssessthrass along with the symbol and get back refined herb.<br>
<br>
Turn the refined herb into Ekmel and receive the symbol of testing.<br>
<br>
hand the symbol of testing into Kazen at this moment a lvl 55 golem will spanw (almost 100% MR) Immediately after the golem ies another weaker mob will spawn and after this mob dies another lvl 55 and will drop the symbol of insanity. Take the symbol of Insanity to Drendico Metalbones in Timerous Deep approx loc +6500,+3800 near the evil docks. He will give you a book with a list of reagents written backwards.<br>
<br>
Translated it says <br>
Must find for Master Kazen<br>
feathered spiroc cloak<br>
eye of innoruuk <br>
slime of blood cazic thule <br>
<br>
Now gather cloak of spiroc feathers in Plane of Sky, Eye of innoruuk from Plane of Hate blood of Cazic Thule from Plane of Fear and retrun it and the journal to Drendico and received a prepared reagent box.<br>
<br>
Take the box back to Kazen and give it to him and he gives you a tome of instruction.<br>
<br>
Go to Plane of Sky and give Thunderspirit Princess 3pp then clear the isle to gorgalosk isle. Give Gkzzallk the tome of instruction and you will get back a gkzzallk in a box (no battle).<br>
<br>
Now go back to Lake Rathe and give Kazen Gkzzallk in a box and receive SCYTHE OF THE SHADOPWED SOUL! YAY!! <br>
